{"tid":1391153,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［香城online］集思廣益 戰術討論","createTime":"2019-07-31T10:46:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T11:03:34.000Z","uid":207294,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0ce90aa02191d8fcf9951a4c9085eda7e18f9753","tid":1391153,"uid":207294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:46:40.000Z","msg":"第一次打咁多文字 排版可能有啲柒請指教 <br />\n有錯請屌細力啲<br />\n<br />\n我眼見個個po都係講online game嘅裝備同糧食<br />\n但我覺得戰術討論不足 幾多裝都唔夠用<br />\n<br />\n打咗幾日細怪<br />\n無錯啲怪嘅攻擊武器實在無咩可能追到<br />\n但發現咗一樣嘢嘅就係<br />\n點解會無目的死守某一啲位到<br />\n可能你會答我要比其他player安全地走game<br />\n但我打機見到嘅係<br />\n點解差不多走咗一大堆人前排得番5行都唔走<br />\n無目的咁死守<br />\n其實為咗啲咩<br />\n<br />\n點解好似做唔返7.1個日齊上齊落咁<br />\n<br />\n其實前排真係好需要策略 好需要溝通<br />\n有陣時守守下都唔知自己做緊啲乜<br />\n<br />\n繼續再咁落去我覺得好多玩家會送頭 跌區etc<br />\n<br />\n有咩其他策略可以做到7.1個日咁有目的有建築物可攻可守<br />\n撚到啲怪 玩家又唔使死<br />\n<br />\n想認真啲討論下 下一步應該點做 如何做到be water嘅精髓<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">光復香港 時代革命</code></pre>"},{"pid":"3ab12fa7c4480788e6a1c6c7272f549e7614316b","tid":1391153,"uid":259613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:56:37.000Z","msg":"打高空戰 弓兵/魔法師上樓射落去"},{"pid":"3faa1833aca3a8caab2276975b5e7d48cff2cc12","tid":1391153,"uid":207294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3ab12fa7c4480788e6a1c6c7272f549e7614316b","tid":1391153,"uid":259613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:56:37.000Z","msg":"打高空戰 弓兵/魔法師上樓射落去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:59:16.000Z","msg":"我都有諗過 既然啲怪都識上天橋<br />\n點解我地唔嘗試下咁樣做<br />\n<br />\n但上樓一定要多人 最驚啲怪會攻上樓<br />\n要係防線被攻破前 通知啲隊友落返樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be9b1cadac26831bab39fb6065f0db3965ecd69a","tid":1391153,"uid":207294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:02:09.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">光復香港 時代革命</code></pre>"},{"pid":"de4d1ded4eeae137be4f815b813be4ae62c8a7b0","tid":1391153,"uid":207294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:02:23.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"cd4efd56cf684c37cbc433262a91b10efcb4ff6e","tid":1391153,"uid":207294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:02:33.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"1a3ea8d69024e624060816d256ebd1879a11de83","tid":1391153,"uid":207294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:02:43.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"57b86f0f3199ec09309ac94bd6008503752fb08c","tid":1391153,"uid":207294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:02:54.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"f321c0cab1de0341af0e25b83fb44998bd81b6b6","tid":1391153,"uid":207294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:03:04.000Z","msg":"時"},{"pid":"9155798db29f5d53b715b779d0dba52697fc2d48","tid":1391153,"uid":207294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:03:14.000Z","msg":"代"},{"pid":"ff472b92ea06c4eefc4ac11e8cf96b58cc5d565e","tid":1391153,"uid":207294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:03:24.000Z","msg":"革"},{"pid":"ac6eaee69163758bb7691416bbb3b6f1c61e0c16","tid":1391153,"uid":207294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:03:34.000Z","msg":"命"}]}